  "title": "System Engineer (Cybersecurity / Network Security)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Highlights:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Permanent job opportunity </strong></li><li><strong>Great remuneration & benefits</strong></li><li><strong>Great career progression</strong></li><li><strong>5 days work week</strong></li><li><strong>Location: Ubi</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Execute technical implementation and configuration tasks.</p></li><li><p>Provide post-deployment support and proactive system maintenance.</p></li><li><p>Develop and maintain clear technical documentation.</p></li><li><p>Support client training and knowledge transfer.</p></li><li><p>Collaborate with cross-functional teams to achieve service excellence.</p></li><li><p>Perform regular system health checks and monitoring.<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Diploma or higher in Computer Engineering, Electrical Engineering, Information Technology, or a related field.</p></li><li><p>1-2 years of experience in technical implementation, support, or a related role.</p></li><li><p>Foundational knowledge of enterprise networking and cybersecurity principles.</p></li><li><p>Hands-on experience installing, testing, and troubleshooting hardware/software.</p></li><li><p>Familiarity with network monitoring tools and basic IT ticketing systems/SLAs.</p></li><li><p>Strong technical writing and client communication skills.</p></li><li><p>A logical, problem-solving mindset with a commitment to learn and improve.</p></li><li><p>Relevant technical certifications (e.g., networking, cloud, cybersecurity) are a strong advantage.</p></li><li><p>Experience in enterprise IT, managed services, or the government sector is beneficial.</p></li></ul><p><strong>HOW TO APPLY:</strong> </p><p>Interested applicants, kindly send your resume in <strong>MS WORD</strong> format to anthony.khoo<a href=\"mailto:dicksern@trustrecruit.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>@trustrecruit.com.sg</strong></a> or please click on “<strong>Apply Now” </strong>and provide the below details in your resume.</p><ul><li>Last drawn salary</li><li>Expected salary</li><li>Notice period</li><li>Reason for leaving</li></ul><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p><strong>Important Note: </strong>Trust Recruit Pte Ltd is committed to safeguarding your personal data in accordance with the Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA). Please read our privacy statement on our corporate website <a href=\"http://www.trustrecruit.com.sg/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">www.trustrecruit.com.sg</a>.</p><p>Trust Recruit Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 19C9950</p><p>EA Personnel: Khoo Choo Xian (Anthony)</p><p>EA Personnel Reg No: R25158524</p>",
